      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bubs tad tas par labb\nkad wiꞥſch juhs peemietle\ngribbat juhs ta winnu peewil\nitt ka kas weenu Zilwekn peewi\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch teefcham juhs fo\ndihs/ ja juhs fleppeni to Watg\nuſluhkejat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Neggi winna Augſti\njuhs iſtrubzina/ un winna Bi\njaſchana jums uſkriht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jubtu Peeminneſchand\nbuhs itt ka Pelni/ un juhsu Aug\nſiba itt ka Mahlu Rohpas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Paleezeet man kluſſu/\nes runnaju/ ka (tahs Sahpes\nmaſkeniht manni pamett.\n"
